{"TopicId":186577,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"The Upcoming Movies (and Movie Trailers) MegaThread!","CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-21T18:35:42Z","PageNum":17,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-21T23:36:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224057975\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186577\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221637533820\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m afraid this \u003Cem\u003Estinks\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the idea... the story. I think it\u0027s hilarious.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut having said that, yeah, I have to agree. I will not run right out and watch it for pretty much every reason you listed\u00A0 \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-11-21T23:36:46Z\u0022 title=\u002211/21/2021 11:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 21, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-21T23:55:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224057997\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186577\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221637537786\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Just Jim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, Just Jim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the idea... the story. I think it\u0027s hilarious.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut having said that, yeah, I have to agree. I will not run right out and watch it for pretty much every reason you listed\u00A0 \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I expect/hope it will fall in the \u0022so bad it\u0027s funny\u0022 category. It almost sounds like something Mel Brooks (or his disciples) could have a hand in, without the over-the-top parody.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-22T06:35:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappily, they released the movie guide.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/XYWq1SP4r-c?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-22T06:36:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0